(ribbons) 

1. N-VAR A ribbon is a long, narrow piece of cloth that you use for tying things together or as a decoration. 装饰带 

例： She had tied back her hair with a peach satin ribbon. 她用一条桃红色的缎带把头发扎在了脑后。 

